title: girl code 101: friend’s exes, calling dibs, awkward situations
itunes:title: girl code 101: friend’s exes, calling dibs, awkward situations
description:
Brooke and Danielle are back and getting into GIRL CODE!!  Is it ok to date your friends ex?  Can you call dibs?  Should you interrupt a convo save your friend who got stuck talking to someone?  The gals read listener stories and share personal experiences with being a gals gal and following the girl code.  Be sure to tag us on your stories + listening screenshots @galsonthegopodcast!
